HEADWORD: Antiscii
<hw>An*tis"ci*i</hw>
<pr>(<?/)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>antiscii</ets>,
Gr. <?/, pl.; <grk>'anti`</grk> against + <?/ shadow.]</ety> <def>The
